#TRANSPORT MODELS AVAILABLE
#
#Model 2d_transportPatchTest Xsize 0.2 Ysize 0.1 minDist 0.005 activeTransport 1 
#Model 3d_transportPatchTest Xsize 0.2 Ysize 0.1 Zsize 0.1 minDist 0.005 activeTransport 1 trials 50000
#Model 3d_BiparvaTubeTransport minDist 0.007 cylinderRad 0.07 cylinderHeight 0.2 tubeThickness 0.02 activeTransport 1 trials 10000 activeMechanics 0
#
